---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { seoMetadata } from '../lib/constants';

const pageMetadata = seoMetadata['/about/'];
---

<BaseLayout title={pageMetadata.title} description={pageMetadata.description}>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_0.8fr] gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
          About Dan
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          I enjoy understanding how things fit together.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          My work sits between operations, websites, digital tools, AI, communication, and conversation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <img
        src="/images/DOT_artist_with_ideas.webp"
        alt=""
        class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-lg object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-16">
      <p>
        The common thread is helping people look carefully at real situations and find a clearer path forward.
      </p>

      <p>
        I do not assume I know the answer before understanding the situation. I listen, ask useful questions, notice patterns, and share what I see.
      </p>

      <p>
        Sometimes the work leads to a website. Sometimes it leads to an operational change. Sometimes it leads to a better decision, a clearer explanation, or simply a stronger sense of what matters next.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Operations experience
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          I spent 21 years inside a large organization coordinating teams, supporting communication, improving operations, training people, interviewing candidates, and working across departments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Digital fluency
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          I build websites, digital tools, and online spaces. I care about digital environments that help people understand who you are, what you do, and why it matters.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
        What I pay attention to
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <p>What is unclear</p>
        <p>What actually matters</p>
        <p>Where coordination is breaking down</p>
        <p>Where people may be operating with different assumptions</p>
        <p>How people find or enter the work</p>
        <p>What digital spaces are communicating</p>
        <p>What structure would help without overcomplicating things</p>
        <p>What might become clearer through conversation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>